The strange watchers are three non-player characters present in the audience during the Mime random event, as well as being featured in the Realm of Memories as Mysterious Watchers, which was part of the 20th Anniversary event. They are the only audience members in the Mime audience.

The three men seemingly represent the three gods; Saradomin, Guthix and Zamorak, resembling statutes of these gods found throughout Gielinor. The order they are seated may represent the order-balance-chaos relationship between these gods, with the Saradomin-esque watcher seated to the east, the Zamorak-esque watcher to the west, with the Guthix-esque watcher in between.
